description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a qualified nurse looking for a few extra hours in one of Merseyside’s largest acute care Trusts?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Would you like to take your first steps into the NHS? If so, we want to hear from you!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Temporary Staffing department is looking for registered nurses to join their team of flexible bank workers who provide temporary cover to all wards and departments within this busy organisation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;All nurses holding a current NMC (Adult) registration are welcome to apply as your skills could be deployed to one of our diverse areas.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Successful applicants will be free to choose their hours of work with shifts including earlies, lates and nights on offer.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Temporary workers are offered the chance to develop their skills, with each registrant given full access the same training as staff substantively employed by the organisation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This is a really exciting opportunity to work in a Trust with an excellent reputation and an exciting future, so don’t delay and apply today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameTemporary Staffing TeamTelephone number0151 529 6999&lt;/p&gt;
